{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SpellWheel is a puzzle-like combat strategy game where you combine together runes to cast spells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/steamshield.gif?t=1734222629\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In battle, each spell you cast further angers your opponent, and each opponent poses its own unique challenge, so choose your actions carefully.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/steamgif.gif?t=1734222629\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout the journey, you will amass an arsenal of magic that will let creative users chain together powerful setups and combos.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/magic2.gif?t=1734222629\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All of this to rescue your beloved from the land of the dead. But the further you go, the more dangerous it becomes as you draw the attention of Death itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/enemies.png?t=1734222629\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intuitive physics-based wheel UI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A  blend of real-time and turn-based combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battles with an emphasis on strategy, planning and making the most of your abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15 uniquely designed hand drawn enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A multi-ending story of either defiance, acceptance, or perhaps a third option</p></li></ul>","backgroun